00:14:25.940 --> 00:14:28.039
Nomor satu, On Jung Sun. Nomor dua, Chef On.

224
00:14:28.039 --> 00:14:30.940
Astaga. Kamu nomor satu di daftar pencarian!

225
00:14:31.639 --> 00:14:33.080
"Apa wajahnya asli?"

